# BlockchainBazaar

## Overview

BlockchainBazaar is your go-to marketplace for all things blockchain. This repository is dedicated to showcasing innovative projects, providing insights into decentralized finance (DeFi), and keeping you updated with the latest news in the cryptocurrency world.

## Features

- **Project Showcase**: Discover groundbreaking blockchain projects.
- **DeFi Insights**: Explore the world of decentralized finance, including yield farming, staking, and liquidity pools.
- **Latest News**: Stay informed with up-to-date cryptocurrency news and trends.
- **Educational Resources**: Access tutorials, articles, and guides on blockchain technology.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

Ensure you have the following installed:
- [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) (version 14 or later)
- [npm](https://www.npmjs.com/) (version 6 or later)

### Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/BlockchainBazaar.git
   cd BlockchainBazaar
